====================================================
TradingGateWay
-long placeOrder((OptionContract,price,quantity,Enum TradeType(buy/sell)) =>return orderId
-long placeOrder(FutureContract,price,quantity,Enum TradeType(buy/sell))
-long placeOrder(stkCode,price,quantity,Enum TradeType(buy/sell))
#for cbbc and warrant, same method call to stock

DataFeedGateWay
->OptionQuote getOptionQuote(OptionContract)
->StockQuote getStockQuote(String code)
->FutureQuote getFutureQuote(FutureContract)
#for cbbc and warrant, same method call to stock

====================================================
Contract definition
====================================================
OptionContract
->String stkCode
->double strikePrice
->Date dueDate(only year and month are effective)
->Enum call/put

FutureContract
->String stkCode
->double stkPrice
->Date dueDate(only year and month are effective)
====================================================
Quote definition
====================================================
OptionQuote
StockQuote
FutureQuote
--> deduce from screen <---

Option:
stkCode
strikePrice
